{"tid":1819464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑貪小便宜得不償失 內地男被劫千二兼受傷","createTime":"2020-01-10T22:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T02:00:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ce713810cf19ea91cd60a28bc3f855ab741149","tid":1819464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:00:44.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時許，一名手持周大福手抽袋的38歲姓周內地男事主，在旺角山東街新填地街交界被一名操普通話的20多歲女子截停，表示有平價房間出租，他不以為意跟隨，並走至百多米外上海街近豉油街一幢大廈內賓館。<br />\n<br />\n男事主繳付200元房租後，發現另一約40歲、同樣操普通話男子在場，稍後發現身上約1萬元現金不見了，懷疑被兩人盜去，三人糾纏期間，男事主成功取回1萬元現金，但被該女子咬傷右手，該對男女乘機逃去。<br />\n<br />\n男事主受傷清醒，事後由救護員送院，手抽袋未有被搶，但點算後發現損失約1,200元。案件列作盜竊及普通襲擊，交由旺角刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕，並正追緝該對男女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VteccJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVteccJa.jpg&h=e4d05f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200111/60472748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60472748&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=1c29bcd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200111%2F60472748&h=7f200ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200111/60472748</a>"},{"pid":"e0d84cc67ad3ea98e9d974b9068b76e6fdde39e8","tid":1819464,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:02:09.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075262595399c22dbc3906b8085a98f514e0cfc8","tid":1819464,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:02:56.000Z","msg":"唉，香港搞到好似以前列強係中原開波咁。<br />\n你哋偷呃拐騙就死返上去做啦。"},{"pid":"0fb5522e4f4f9f0ad8bea545c7f971223c839790","tid":1819464,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T22:05:37.000Z","m